<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  {% include "_google_tag.html.j2" %}

  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ seo.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ seo.description }}">
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ seo.canonical }}">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,follow">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root { --navy: #002b5e; --ink: #111; --muted: #555; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink); margin: 0; padding: 24px 0 40px; background: #c8c8c2; line-height: 1.5; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    .toolbar { max-width: 190mm; margin: 0 auto 16px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #b0b0a8; border-top: 4px solid var(--navy); border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 18px; }
    .toolbar h1 { font-size: 16px; color: var(--navy); margin: 0 0 6px; }
    .toolbar p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 10px; }
    .toolbar .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .toolbar button { font-family: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 3px; cursor: pointer; }
    .toolbar .pri { background: #cc0000; color: #fff; border: 0; }
    .toolbar .sec { background: #fff; color: var(--navy); border: 1px solid var(--navy); }
    .toolbar a.back { color: var(--navy); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
    .sheet { max-width: 190mm; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; padding: 14mm 16mm; box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
    h1.doc-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .lbl-en { display: inline; }
    .lbl-es { display: none; }
    .en-guide { background: #eef4ff; border: 1px solid #c5d4f0; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 14px; margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.55; color: #222; }
    .en-guide strong { color: var(--navy); }
    .p-wrap { font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 1.6; }
    .p-wrap p { margin: 0 0 14px; }
    .inline { display: inline-block; min-width: 80px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.5pt; padding: 0 2px 1px; border: 0; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #333; background: #fff7c2; max-width: 100%; }
    .sign-row { margin-top: 20px; }
    .sign-row .lbl { display: block; font-size: 10pt; color: #444; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .sign-row .line { min-height: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .sig-cursive { font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive; font-size: 32px; min-height: 36px; line-height: 1.1; color: #000; }
    .bot-fields { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .bot-fields { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .bot-fields label { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; }
    .bot-fields input { width: 100%; font-family: inherit; font-size: 11pt; padding: 2px; border: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; background: #fff7c2; }
    @page { size: A4; margin: 12mm; }
    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; padding: 0; }
      .toolbar, .no-print-elm, .en-guide { display: none !important; }
      .sheet { box-shadow: none; max-width: none; padding: 0; }
      .inline, .bot-fields input { background: transparent !important; }
      #dsig-in { display: none !important; }
      #dsig-out { display: block !important; }
      .lbl-en { display: none !important; }
      .lbl-es { display: inline !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="toolbar">
    <h1>Sworn declaration (no criminal record) — English help, Spanish PDF</h1>
    <p>
      Use the blue box for <strong>what to type</strong>. The declaration body prints in <strong>Spanish</strong>
      with your answers inserted — that is what most consulates and Cancillería Digital expect.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <button type="button" class="pri" onclick="window.print()">Print / Save as PDF</button>
      <button type="button" class="sec" onclick="window.location.reload()">Reset</button>
      <a class="back" href="/declaracion-jurada-visa-venezolana">What is a declaración jurada?</a>
      <a class="back" href="/apply-for-venezuelan-visa">← Full visa guide (2026)</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <form class="sheet" id="dform" autocomplete="off" lang="es">
    <h1 class="doc-title"><span class="lbl-en">Sworn declaration (no criminal record)</span><span class="lbl-es" lang="es">Declaración jurada</span></h1>

    <div class="en-guide no-print-elm">
      <strong>What you are filling in</strong> (answers can be in English; the printed wording stays official Spanish):
      <ul style="margin:8px 0 0 18px;padding:0;">
        <li><strong>Full name</strong> — first blank (appears after “Yo,”).</li>
        <li><strong>Country of citizenship</strong> — second blank (after “ciudadano de los”).</li>
        <li><strong>Passport number</strong> — third blank.</li>
        <li>The printed document states you have <strong>no criminal record</strong> in your home country or elsewhere, for your Venezuelan visa application.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="p-wrap">
      <p>
        Yo,
        <input class="inline" id="dnombre" name="dnombre" type="text" placeholder="full legal name" style="min-width: 200px; width: min(100%, 320px)">,
        ciudadano de los
        <input class="inline" id="dcountry" name="dcountry" type="text" placeholder="country of citizenship" style="min-width: 160px; width: min(100%, 280px)">,
        titular del pasaporte No.
        <input class="inline" id="dpass" name="dpass" type="text" placeholder="passport number" style="min-width: 120px; width: min(100%, 200px)">,
        declaro bajo juramento que no poseo antecedentes penales en mi país de origen ni en ningún otro país.
      </p>
      <p>
        La presente declaración se realiza a los fines de cumplir con los requisitos de solicitud de visa
        ante las autoridades de la República Bolivariana de Venezuela.
      </p>
      <p>
        Declaro que la información aquí suministrada es verdadera y autorizo su verificación.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="sign-row">
      <span class="lbl no-print-elm" style="font-size:10pt;">
        <span class="lbl-en">Signature — type your full name (prints in cursive):</span>
        <span class="lbl-es" lang="es">Firma (escriba su nombre; se muestra en cursiva al imprimir):</span>
      </span>
      <div class="no-print-elm" style="margin:6px 0 4px;">
        <input type="text" id="dsig-in" class="inline" style="min-width: 260px; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; font-size: 14px; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" placeholder="Full legal name for signature">
      </div>
      <div id="dsig-out" class="sig-cursive" style="min-height:40px; margin: 4px 0 0;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="bot-fields">
      <div>
        <label for="dnb"><span class="lbl-en">Printed name (match above)</span><span class="lbl-es" lang="es">Nombre (impreso)</span></label>
        <input id="dnb" type="text" placeholder="Same as full name above">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="dfecha"><span class="lbl-en">Date</span><span class="lbl-es" lang="es">Fecha</span></label>
        <input id="dfecha" type="text" placeholder="e.g. April 23, 2026">
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>

  <script>
  function syncDSig() {
    var i = document.getElementById('dsig-in'), o = document.getElementById('dsig-out');
    if (i && o) o.textContent = (i && i.value) ? i.value : '';
  }
  var si = document.getElementById('dsig-in');
  if (si) si.addEventListener('input', syncDSig);
  syncDSig();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
